T1  - Effects of Emotional Disability and Clear Performance Standards on Performance Ratings
AU  - Czajka, Joseph M.
AU  - DeNisi, Angelo S.
Y1  - 1988/06/01
PY  - 1988
DA  - 1988/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/256555
