T1  - Personal Control as a Mediator Between Perceptions of Supervisory Behaviors and Employee Reactions
AU  - Greenberger, David B.
AU  - Strasser, Stephen
AU  - Lee, Soonmook
Y1  - 1988/06/01
PY  - 1988
DA  - 1988/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/256556
